---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Dan — Dan Tremblay Music"
  description="Learn about Dan Tremblay — Ottawa piano instructor, producer, and composer with three decades of teaching and music experience."
  solidNav={true}
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="page-hero-content">
      <div class="page-eyebrow">Piano Instructor · Producer · Ottawa</div>
      <h1 class="page-title">About Dan</h1>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost-sm">Book Your Free Lesson</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HISTORY -->
  <section class="history">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="history-grid">
        <div class="history-main">
          <span class="eyebrow">History</span>
          <h2 class="section-h">Three Decades of Music &amp; Teaching</h2>
          <p class="body-text">
            Based in Ottawa, Canada, Dan Tremblay has become known as much for his blend of ambient
            and electronic music as for his music instruction. Having gotten an early start under the
            careful guidance of his mother, he has since shared his several decades of musical
            knowledge with hundreds of students. On 8 occasions, his students have received
            provincial awards for the highest mark in their respective grade in piano performance.
            His teaching has since expanded to <a
              href="https://dan-s-site-8ede.thinkific.com/collections"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">online course offerings</a
            > covering topics including piano improvisation and cinematic music production.
          </p>
          <p class="body-text">
            Pivoting to <a
              href="https://www.twitch.tv/dantremblaymusic"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">online performance on Twitch</a
            > in 2021 led to numerous production and mixing opportunities for international artists.
            This time also sparked a flurry of cinematic album releases under his own name, as well
            as several collaborations, including a song to be featured in an upcoming VR game.
          </p>
          <p class="body-text">
            His instrumental compositions ranging from delicate and sparse piano, to epic and
            cinematic have been licensed worldwide.
          </p>
          <p class="body-text">
            Recently, his <a
              href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRKCH91U2AhotO9nTlQP5OQ"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">YouTube channel</a
            > has garnered attention from both composers and audio developers alike. This resulted in
            production work for New Zealand born composer, Christopher Norton, as well as content
            creation and commissioned work for Emergence Audio. He regularly reviews products for
            Fracture Sounds, Soundiron, Westwood Instruments, Sonixinema, Frozen Plain, Slate &amp;
            Ash, Field Tone Audio and Filine Technologies.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-navy" style="margin-top:10px">Book a Free Lesson</a>
        </div>
        <div class="history-sidebar">
          <img
            src="/images/dan-tremblay.jpeg"
            alt="Dan Tremblay"
            class="sidebar-photo"
          />
          <div class="awards-card">
            <div class="awards-title">Awards &amp; Highlights</div>
            <div class="award-item"><span class="award-dash"></span>8× Provincial Piano Awards</div>
            <div class="award-item"><span class="award-dash"></span>30+ Years Teaching</div>
            <div class="award-item">
              <span class="award-dash"></span>Published Multimedia Composer
            </div>
            <div class="award-item"><span class="award-dash"></span>Global Music Licenses</div>
            <div class="award-item"><span class="award-dash"></span>YouTube Creator</div>
            <div class="award-item"><span class="award-dash"></span>Twitch Performer</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STUDENT VIDEO -->
  <section class="video-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="video-header">
        <span class="eyebrow">Student Testimonials</span>
        <h2 class="section-h" style="text-align:center;margin-top:10px">
          Hear From Dan's Students
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="video-wrap">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ"
          title="Student Testimonial — Dan Tremblay Music"
          allowfullscreen
          loading="lazy"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LONG QUOTE -->
  <section class="quote-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="long-quote">
        <span class="quote-opener">"</span>
        <p class="quote-body">
          I've been with him since the very beginning during my days as a student with Music for
          Young Children and have never wanted to switch instructors once, even now with Mr. Dan
          helping me complete grade 8 piano for Conservatory Canada. I could go on and on about why
          Mr. Dan is the absolute best, but here's a quick summary on why Dan's the man when it
          comes to piano. Every lesson he makes me smile or laugh with something he's said at some
          point. He's non judgmental and encouraging during practice sessions, and is always giving
          great constructive criticism that I can apply through the week before coming back the next
          week. Aside from the recitals he hosts where his students play every year, Mr. Dan is an
          excellent performer himself and is very talented at more than just the piano. I highly
          recommend checking him out!
        </p>
        <p class="quote-attr">— Everett, Student for 11 years</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="cta-h">Ready to Learn Piano?</h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-outline-white">Book Your Lesson</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* PAGE HERO */
  .page-hero {
    padding-top: 64px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 340px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .page-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url('/images/piano.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center 40%;
  }
  .page-hero-bg::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(5, 11, 27, 0.78) 0%, rgba(5, 11, 27, 0.62) 100%);
  }
  .page-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 64px clamp(20px, 5vw, 64px);
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .page-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.42);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: block;
  }
  .page-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 76px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: white;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .btn-ghost-sm {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 11px 28px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.38);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    transition: border-color 0.18s, color 0.18s;
  }
  .btn-ghost-sm:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    color: white;
  }

  /* TYPOGRAPHY */
  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: #4b5e92;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: block;
  }
  .section-h {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(30px, 3vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.12;
    color: #0d1120;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .body-text {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #5c6580;
    line-height: 1.8;
    text-wrap: pretty;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .body-text a {
    color: #4b5e92;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.18s;
  }
  .body-text a:hover {
    border-color: #4b5e92;
  }

  /* BUTTONS */
  .btn-navy {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 13px 28px;
    background: #050b1b;
    color: white;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    transition:
      background 0.18s,
      transform 0.14s;
  }
  .btn-navy:hover {
    background: #4b5e92;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  /* HISTORY */
  .history {
    padding: 96px 0;
    background: #eff5fc;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(20px, 5vw, 64px);
  }
  .history-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .sidebar-photo {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .awards-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid rgba(13, 17, 32, 0.1);
    padding: 22px;
  }
  .awards-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #0d1120;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .award-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #5c6580;
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(13, 17, 32, 0.1);
  }
  .award-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .award-dash {
    width: 14px;
    height: 1px;
    background: #4b5e92;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: block;
  }

  /* VIDEO */
  .video-section {
    padding: 96px 0;
    background: white;
  }
  .video-section .container {
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  .video-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .video-wrap {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%;
    height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #050b1b;
  }
  .video-wrap iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: none;
  }

  /* QUOTE */
  .quote-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #eff5fc;
  }
  .quote-section .container {
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  .long-quote {
    padding: 44px 52px;
    background: white;
    border-top: 2px solid #4b5e92;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(5, 11, 27, 0.06);
  }
  .quote-opener {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 88px;
    color: #4b5e92;
    line-height: 0.55;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    opacity: 0.35;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .quote-body {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(15px, 1.8vw, 19px);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #0d1120;
    line-height: 1.75;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .quote-attr {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #5c6580;
    margin-top: 22px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* CTA BAND */
  .cta-band {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #4b5e92;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .cta-h {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 3.5vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .btn-outline-white {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 14px 40px;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    color: white;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition:
      background 0.18s,
      border-color 0.18s;
  }
  .btn-outline-white:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-color: white;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .history-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .sidebar-photo {
      max-width: 340px;
    }
    .long-quote {
      padding: 28px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
